Module kivakit.interfaces
Package com.telenav.kivakit.interfaces.numeric

Interface RandomNumeric

All Superinterfaces:
CastTrait
public interface RandomNumeric extends CastTrait
Provides convenient random number methods given an implementation of randomLongExclusive(long, long), and randomDoubleZeroToOne(). Methods that end in "exclusive" do not include the given maximum value. Methods that end in "inclusive" do include the given maximum value.
Author:
jonathanl (shibo)
